Class NonPlayerCharacter

java.lang.Object
GameCharacter
NonPlayerCharacter
public class NonPlayerCharacter extends GameCharacter
This is our NonPlayer Character that inherits from GameCharacter it represent objects the game controls (as opposed to objects a human player controls).
